com.innowhere.jnieasy.core.method
Interface NativeFieldMethod

All Superinterfaces:
NativeBehavior, NativeCapable
All Known Subinterfaces:
CFieldMethod, NativeDirectFieldCallback, NativeDirectInstanceFieldCallback, NativeDirectStaticFieldCallback, NativeFieldCallback, NativeFieldMethodReflection, NativeInstanceFieldCallback, NativeInstanceFieldMethod, NativeInstanceFieldMethodReflection, NativeStaticFieldCallback, NativeStaticFieldMethod, NativeStaticFieldMethodReflection
public interface NativeFieldMethod
extends NativeBehavior

The NativeFieldMethod is the interface implemented by native capable classes that bridges Java and native fields seen as methods.

Author:
Jose M. Arranz Santamaria
